{"word":"Jewels","slug":"jewels","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jewels</b> Betrothal presents of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=53'>Gen 24:53</a><br/> Borrowed from Egyptians by Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=22'>Exo 3:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=11&verse=2'>Exo 11:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=35'>Exo 12:35</a><br/> Dedicated to the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=35&verse=22'>Exo 35:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=52'>Num 31:52</a><br/> Regarded by Jacob as obnoxious to holiness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=4'>Gen 35:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=6'>Exo 33:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=21'>Isa 3:21</a><br/> Tokens of love<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=16&verse=13'>Eze 16:13</a><br/> Worn by men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=23&verse=42'>Eze 23:42</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=20&verse=15'>Pro 20:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=17'>Mal 3:17</a><br/><a href='S:Bracelet'>Bracelet</a>; <a href='S:Chains'>Chains</a>; <a href='S:Ear-Ring'>Ear-Ring</a>; <a href='S:Muffler'>Muffler</a>; <a href='S:Pearl'>Pearl</a>; <a href='S:Ring'>Ring</a>; <a href='S:Seal'>Seal</a>; <a href='S:Stones, Precious'>Stones, Precious</a>"}]}